name: Uh-oh! (V)
Lore: 'Imperial law had no place in the Hutt''s domain.',
Text: 'Deploy on table.  Once per turn, may use 1 Force to deploy one Clak''dor VII, Neb Dulo, or a musician from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.  While you control Clak''dor VII, your musicians are power and forfeit +2.  During your control phase, may retrieve 1 Force for each battleground site you control with a musician. (Immune to Alter.)(Errata Text - September 9th, 2009)',
